</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the right hand side cover of the media drawer (8 screws). 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-D573907F-2A43-46C0-B997-42F943FF57D2" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-40E67322-D9BF-49F8-BD8D-91F0B7792871-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-40E67322-D9BF-49F8-BD8D-91F0B7792871-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 4 screws of the motor assembly. 
