</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Disconnect the spring from the assembly. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_5995505077A64032AAA49C0747A36A3B" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-67925573-FA11-4527-AD6B-9783BBBCC279-low.png" id="IMAGE_C6D3D7F7D5794963BB328DB93C498CD0" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-67925573-FA11-4527-AD6B-9783BBBCC279-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
