</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Slide the motor out of the drawer. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="FIG_80E9E01CBEC04F869BF972CC71BF857A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-29A5EE70-F4AB-40A0-8491-9676E865F614-low.png" id="IMAGE_ABEFA9FABC5F47928E71BDA4B7A7BBFC" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-29A5EE70-F4AB-40A0-8491-9676E865F614-low.png"/></fig><fig id="FIG_FACC899373BF471785A34A2BB35F66C1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-34C35387-2477-4B43-B3F5-AA7B1DEC17FD-low.png" id="IMAGE_8DD17F857CAC424FAE221D8DF92CD0FB" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-34C35387-2477-4B43-B3F5-AA7B1DEC17FD-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_F77204E29D3E4F6D8F3503958683C72F" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
